posting_body: ['Austin, 78757', 'West Anderson Lane', '$913', '1 Bedroom', '***Availability and pricing is real-time, can change daily, and varies by lease term***', 'These apartments feature a living room, dining room, and a kitchen with standard appliances, standard countertops, a dishwasher, and disposal.', 'There is hardwood flooring in the living area, the kitchen, and the bedroom(s), with tile in the bathroom(s).', 'Features central A/C, central heat, ceiling fans, lighting fixtures, window blinds, and walk-in closets.', 'Select units have patio/balcony.', 'Community amenities include business center, dog park, pool, sundeck, clubhouse, and on-site laundry.', 'Pets welcome.', 'Off-street parking available.', 'An eight-minute drive to Interstate 35.', 'PHOTOS ARE AN EXAMPLE OF SIMILAR UNITS WITHIN THE BUILDING, ACTUAL UNIT MAY VARY.', 'Contact Agent:', 'Dave Burroughs', 'Independent Agents Austin TX', 'show contact info', 'Follow us on Twitter @RentalBeast', 'Find us on Facebook: <URL>']
